               <code code="34067-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="INDICATIONS &amp; USAGE SECTION"/>
               <title>
                  <content styleCode="bold"> INDICATIONS
</content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Tetrofosmin is a diagnostic agent used to assess areas of reversible myocardial ischemia in the presence or absence of infracted myocardium and is also used to assess ventricular function.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">PHYSICAL HALF-LIFE &amp; TARGET ORGANS</content>
                  </paragraph>
